###Get All inquiries
GET http://localhost:3000/inquiries

###Get inquiry by id
GET http://localhost:3000/inquiries/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID

###Get inquiries by status - pending
GET http://localhost:3000/inquiries/by-status/pending

###Get inquiries by status - in-progress
GET http://localhost:3000/inquiries/by-status/in-progress

###Get inquiries by status - resolved
GET http://localhost:3000/inquiries/by-status/resolved

###Get inquiries by status - closed
GET http://localhost:3000/inquiries/by-status/closed

###Create inquiry
POST http://localhost:3000/inquiries
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Sarah Johnson",
    "email": "sarah.johnson@example.com",
    "phone": "780-555-1234",
    "subject": "Question about Event Schedule",
    "message": "Hi, I was wondering if there will be any breaks during the day-long activities? My daughter has some dietary restrictions and needs to eat at specific times.",
    "status": "pending"
}

